Date: Mon, 18 May 2026 04:22:10 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 1/2] M384-M393: Extract histogram/registry/grid into dedicated
 kernels, scope reduce to SP group
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

M384: sp_dp_registry — extract get_sp_group() dedicated accessor
M385: bloombee_bridge — fix DHT wildcard→registry pattern, extract _update_registry
M386: sp_histogram — scope reduce_histograms to SP group (was default/world)
M387: hetero_mesh — add FP8 dtype validation, extract _build_*_groups from plan_hetero_mesh
M388: occupancy_grid — extract capability_from_tier_info for remote-aware grid sizing
M389: double_buffer_a2a — add _COLLECTIVE_LOCK for NCCL serialization
M390: all_to_all — strip dead patterns
M391: sp_compile — deterministic BFS via sorted seed_nodes, ndim>=3 guard on mask tag
M392: constants — add FP8 dtypes to AUTOSP_SUPPORTED_DTYPES
M393: verify + commit

8 files changed, +176 -69

Signed-off-by: dylanyunlon <dylanyunlong@gmail.com>
