From 6abffeb948a397029feb0c08137b71552326744c Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: dylanyunlon <dylanyunlong@gmail.com>
Date: Mon, 18 May 2026 04:28:09 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 2/2] M394-M395: Add 13B model config (48L/36H/4608D=12.46B) +
 ags1 experiment script
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

M394: Add 13B to model configs and argparse choices
  - Architecture: 48 layers, 36 heads, 4608 dim = 12.46B params
  - n_head=36 divisible by 3 → SP works on 3-GPU ags1 cluster
  - BF16 model = 24.9GB → fits A6000 48GB with 23GB headroom for AC
  - Requires: --cpu_offload --use_ac (optimizer states on CPU)

M395: Create run_13B_ags1.sh experiment script
  - Phase 0: Smoke test (5 steps, verify OOM-free)
  - Phase 1: DDP baseline (Kx=1, 200 steps)
  - Phase 2: DES-LOC Kx ablation (Kx=16/32/64, 200 steps)
  - Phase 3: DES-LOC + AutoSP (SP memory savings → try bs=2)
  - Phase 4: Long-run (1536 steps, best Kx)
  - Phase 5: Nesterov outer optimizer
  - All phases: bs=1 grad_accum=8, --cpu_offload --use_ac

Memory analysis (per GPU):
  A6000: 24.9GB model + ~1GB AC activations = ~26GB / 48GB available
  H100:  24.9GB model + ~1GB AC activations = ~26GB / 96GB available
  Optimizer: CPU-offloaded (~100GB host RAM for Adam m+v+fp32 master)

Signed-off-by: dylanyunlon <dylanyunlong@gmail.com>
